## Evrensel Optimizasyon Kuralları (3 Config'e de Uygulanır)

```python
# 1. VRAM Temizleme — Her inference sonrası
torch.cuda.empty_cache()

# 2. Nomic Q8 — 4bit context,
8bit weights hybrid
model.load(quantization="q8_0", context_offload=True)

# 3. Jina Reranker — ONNX CPU, VRAM açık bırak
reranker = load_onnx("jina-reranker-v2", device="cpu")

# 4. LanceDB — IVF-PQ index, memory-mapped
db = lancedb.connect("./lance_store", read_consistency_interval=0)

# 5. Mem0 — async write, sync read
await mem0.add_async(memory, user_id=session_id)
```

